      "writtenOn": "2019-07-09T08:52:47Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "To run *prebuilt* private tests downloaded as an archive, we run: tast run -build\u003dfalse -downloadprivatebundles ...\n\nTo run *fresh* private tests built from source, we run: tast run -buildbundle\u003dcrosint ...\n\nNote that -downloadprivatebundles is a flag to download an archive of *prebuilt* private bundles.\n\nDoes this explanation clarify it?",
